Privacy Policy for SERP Feature Analyzer
Last updated: March 8, 2026
SERP Feature Analyzer ("the Extension") is a Chrome browser extension designed to analyze search engine results pages (SERPs) and identify visible SERP features. This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use the Extension.
1. Data Collection
SERP Feature Analyzer does not collect, store, or transmit personal data.
The Extension analyzes the content of the active search results page directly within the user's browser in order to detect and display SERP features. All processing occurs locally on the user's device.
The Extension does not collect information such as:
Names
Email addresses
IP addresses
Location data
Search history outside the active page
Personally identifiable information
2. Data Storage
The Extension may use Chrome's built-in local storage to save user preferences or settings. This data remains on the user's device and is not transmitted to any external servers.
3. Data Transmission
SERP Feature Analyzer does not transmit any data from the user's browser to external servers.
All analysis and processing performed by the Extension happens locally within the browser environment.
4. Third-Party Services
The Extension does not use third-party analytics services, tracking technologies, advertising networks, or external APIs that collect user data.
5. Permissions
The Extension may request certain browser permissions in order to function properly. These permissions are used solely to enable the Extension's features.
For example:
activeTab – Allows the Extension to analyze the currently active search results page when the user activates the extension.
storage – Allows the Extension to save user preferences locally within the browser.
These permissions are used only for the functionality of the Extension and not for collecting personal information.
6. Children's Privacy
The Extension is not directed toward children under the age of 13 and does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any updates will be posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date.
